text: Michel Bertraneu (born 26 October 1949) is a French equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
